==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Pains
<hw>Pains</hw> <pr>(p⟦amac⟧nz)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Labor; toilsome
effort; care or trouble taken; -- plural in form, but used with a
singular or plural verb, commonly the former.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>And all my <qex>pains</qex> is sorted to no proof.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The <qex>pains</qex> they had taken was very great.</q>
<rj><qau>Clarendon.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The labored earth your <qex>pains</qex> have sowed and tilled.</q>
<rj><qau>Dryden.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Painstaker</ent>⟦br⟧
